5.1.2 Lambdas and collections
	- good programming style -> avoid duplication in your code.

	- "selector logic" 
		-> receives a collection element as an argument and returns a value to compare.
			ex)
				================================================
				data class Person(val age: Int)

				val list = listOf(Person(1), Person(2), Person(3))

				list.maxByOrNull { it.age } // selector logic
				================================================

	

